snippet.title: Planet Alpha - E3 2018 Unlock the Mysteries | PS4
snippet.description:
You find yourself stranded on an alien planet. Strange beings, cryptic clues and the overwhelming environment stand in your way, as you try to uncover the mysteries which lurk beneath the surface of PLANET ALPHA!         

Coming to PlayStation 4 in 2018

Follow Planet Alpha on Twitter: https://twitter.com/PLANETALPHA 
Follow Planet Alpha on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/planetalpha/ 

About Team17 Digital Ltd
Founded in 1990, Team17 Digital Limited is a leading international games label that hosts the Worms franchise, Yooka-Laylee, The Escapists, Overcooked, Genesis: Alpha One, and many more from amazing developers around the world. Visit www.team17.com for more info.

Don't forget you can also -
Like us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Team17/
Follow us on Twitter: http://bit.ly/FollowT17
